{"tid":510149,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[曹星如畢生宿敵]怪物拳王井上尚弥即將出戰來自法國的挑戰者","createTime":"2017-12-26T07:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T11:21:52.000Z","uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"19e2807598d08f8bcc2265089893649d28f9fac4","tid":510149,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"#拳擊新聞<br />\n<br />\n當今 WBO super flyweight 拳王 井上尚弥 (Naoya Inoue) 14-0-0 (12 KOs) 將於台灣時間這周六 (12/30) 下午 6:00 於日本東京進行第 7 次頭銜防衛戰，出戰來自法國的 Yoan Boyeaux 41-4-0 (26 KOs)，擔綱當天[img]圖片網址[/img]賽事的主賽。<br />\n<br />\n與他的綽號 &ldquo;怪物&rdquo;如出一轍，年僅 24 歲的 井上尚弥，已經是稱霸二個量級的拳王。職業生涯第 4 場賽事隨即挑戰 OPBF (東太平洋) flyweight 拳王頭銜，第 5 場職業賽奪下 WBC flyweight 拳王頭銜，一度創下日本國內史上以最少職業賽場次奪下世界拳王頭銜紀錄，之後在 2014 年，12 月提升量級到 115 磅量級 (super flyweight)，挑戰當時的 WBO 拳王 Omar Andres Narvaez，並奪下拳王頭銜，那場賽事是他的第 8 場職業賽，一度創下最少場次奪下二個量級拳王頭銜紀錄。<br />\n <br />\n或許 井上尚弥 明年有機會挑戰曹星如，但得看這周末對上 Boyeaux 是否能夠全身而退。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mainichi.jp/vol1/2017/12/20/20171220k0000e050319000p/6.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.mainichi.jp%2Fvol1%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F20171220k0000e050319000p%2F6.jpg%3F1&h=113e3dfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67e9676372ddc54b8eb80127af208fa169a47607","tid":510149,"uid":14497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"井上尚弥 明年有機會挑戰曹星如 痴撚線"},{"pid":"4d997481420119a5c15cacc1ba7628095d4fcf05","tid":510149,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"井上尚弥 明年有機會挑戰曹星如<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8f12e7ffcf59e32794fdee1683f114c852f5e2","tid":510149,"uid":4957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4d997481420119a5c15cacc1ba7628095d4fcf05","tid":510149,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-